dcterms:creator: C. McCollough
dcterms:description: The Low Dose CT Grand Challenge dataset includes medical imaging data aimed at evaluating low dose computed tomography techniques. It provides images at 1 mm slice thickness, with a specific division of patients for training, validation, and testing.
dcterms:title: Low Dose CT Grand Challenge

dcterms:description: This dataset consists of images from the first seven patients for training, the next two for validation, and the last patient for testing, derived from the Low Dose CT Grand Challenge.
dcterms:title: Images from Low Dose CT Grand Challenge
